Citizens First Bancorp.

Inc talk sey e don gree buy Lakeland First Financial Group Inc, Succasunna, N.J. bank holding company, na about $50.6 million inside cash, and stock.

Citizens first wey be Citizens First National Bank, wey dey base for Glen Rock, N.J. go pay di maximum of 40% money for di parent of Lakeland Savings Bank, plus di remaining one for convertible stock wey be $18 liquidation.

Lakeland holders go get option, wheder na stock, or cash.

Di convertible preferred to pay dividend for di 7.875%, and convertible to share Citizens First, at di rate of 20% increase for di stock during 20 days before di transaction finish.

Di deal na for regulatory, and shareholder approval.

